name: Sunshine Stone Necklace
description:
Long Gold chain with a unique Sunshine Stone.  Sunshine Stone, is Florida Agatized Coral, from the ancient coral reef that sat on top of Florida over 35 million years ago.  When the state rose from the water, the coral fossilized and is now Florida's State Stone. 
Note: these are made to order so I stay true to the design of the necklace shown, but each stones varies.  I will cut you the best stone possible to represent what you see in the picture!
